
extends ./templates/main.pug

block content

  .container
    img(src="M4_logo.png" alt="Timestamp Logo")
  .container
    h2 API Project: Image Search Abstraction Layer - Express
    h3 User Stories:
    ol
      li I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.
      li I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.
      li I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.
    h3 Example Usage
    ul
      li <a href="#{apilink}/cats?offset=10">#{home}/#{apilink}/cats?offset=10</a>
      li <a href="#{apilink}/latest">#{home}/#{apilink}/latest</a>
